Package: funestim
Type: Package
Title: Nonparametric Kernel Smoothing Methods for Functional Data
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2019-04-26
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
Authors@R: person("Steven", "Golovkine", 
                email = "steven_golovkine@icloud.com", 
                role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Steven Golovkine <steven_golovkine@icloud.com>
Description: Nonparametric kernel smoothing methods that perform adaptive
  optimal estimation of irregular mean and covariance functions in functional
  data context. Code for the paper `Adaptive optimal estimation of irregular
  mean and covariance functions`, S. Golovkine, N. Klutchnikoff, V. Patilea
  (2021).
